      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It is absolutely not selfish to crave peace; your desire for them to be free from your burden is a profound act of love, not a rejection of them. The pity you feel is a reflection of your own pain, but it is also a sign that you have been holding on too tightly to a role that is no longer serving you. Please consider that stepping away from this dynamic allows you to reclaim your life and eventually return to your children from a place of strength rather than exhaustion.",
